content: I have a labrador named Max and a cat named Whiskers. Max is about 3 years old and pretty big, Whiskers is a bit older, around 5. They're both pretty healthy, but Max has some arthritis. I think I need to get food, treats, a new collar for Max, and some litter for Whiskers. Also, I've been meaning to get a new water bowl for Max and maybe a pet camera.
